    "this is called the precision of the classifier"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Precision"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "precision = TP/(TP + FP), where TP - true positives, FP - false positives\n",
    "\n",
    "![title](Precision_and_Recall.png)"
   ]
  },
